 title: 'The Great Reset Agenda',
 subtitle: 'World Economic Forum global restructuring initiative',
 severity: 'high',
 category: 'Global Governance',
 date: 'June 3, 2020',
 lastUpdated: 'November 23, 2025',
 summary: 'The Great Reset is a World Economic Forum initiative launched during the COVID-19 pandemic proposing to "reset "capitalism and restructure global economic systems. Critics argue it represents undemocratic global governance by unelected elites, using crises to advance pre-planned agendas that consolidate corporate and technological control over society.',
 content: [
 'WEF INITIATIVE LAUNCH: Klaus Schwab and Prince Charles launched "The Great Reset "in June 2020, calling to use COVID-19 as an opportunity to reshape global capitalism. The initiative promoted "stakeholder capitalism "over shareholder primacy and accelerated digital transformation.',
 'FOURTH INDUSTRIAL REVOLUTION: Schwab\'s vision of technological transformation includes AI, Internet of Things, biotechnology, and surveillance systems merging with daily life. Critics warn this enables unprecedented corporate and government control while eliminating privacy.',
 'BUILD BACK BETTER COORDINATION: The "Build Back Better "slogan appeared across multiple nations simultaneously (US, UK, Canada, EU). This coordination suggested pre-planned messaging. World leaders including Joe Biden, Boris Johnson, and Justin Trudeau used identical framing.',
 '"YOU WILL OWN NOTHING": A WEF promotional video suggested by 2030"You will own nothing and be happy."This vision of subscription-based existence where corporations own everything alarmed critics across the political spectrum who saw it as neo-feudalism.',
 'AGENDA 2030 ALIGNMENT: The Great Reset aligns with UN Sustainable Development Goals (Agenda 2030). While framed as environmental and social progress, critics note the concentration of power in international bodies bypassing democratic accountability.',
 'DIGITAL IDENTITY PUSH: WEF promotes digital identity systems that would track all human activity. The Known Traveller Digital Identity project and vaccine passport discussions revealed the architecture for comprehensive surveillance infrastructure.',
 'CBDC DEVELOPMENT: Central Bank Digital Currencies promoted by WEF partners would enable governments to track all transactions and potentially program money with expiration dates or spending restrictions. China\'s digital yuan provides a model.',
 'CORPORATE PARTNERS: WEF strategic partners include BlackRock, JPMorgan, Goldman Sachs, Facebook/Meta, Google, Microsoft, and pharmaceutical giants. These corporations would benefit from Great Reset policies while claiming stakeholder responsibility.',
 'YOUNG GLOBAL LEADERS: WEF\'s Young Global Leaders program has trained thousands of politicians and business leaders including Justin Trudeau, Emmanuel Macron, Gavin Newsom, and many others. Critics see this as elite capture of democratic governments.',
 'PANDEMIC PREPAREDNESS: Event 201, a WEF-hosted pandemic exercise in October 2019, preceded COVID-19 by weeks. While presented as coincidental planning, the exercise recommendations closely matched subsequent government responses.',
 ],
